Success Nwogu, Abuja The National Secretary of the  Peoples Democratic Party, Senator  Ibrahim Tsauri, on Wednesday said the party will hold an emergency National Executive Meeting  on Thursday. He added that the meeting would hold at the PDP National Secretariat, Wadata Plaza, Abuja In a statement, he also said the meeting would commence from 3pm. Copyright PUNCH.
